# type(scope): Subject in imperative mood (≤72 chars)
#
# Types: feat fix refactor perf docs test ci build chore revert
# Scope: optional, lowercase noun for the subsystem (e.g., cl-llm, telegram)
#
# --- Subject rules ---
# - Imperative mood: "Add" not "Added"
# - Capitalize after colon
# - No trailing period
# - One commit = one logical change
#
# Body: explain WHY, not how. Wrap at 72 chars.
# 1. What was the problem or motivation?
# 2. What does this change enable?
# 3. Non-obvious side effects?
#
# Footers (git trailer format):
#   Closes: bd-42
#   Fixes: bd-17
#   Refs: bd-99
#   BREAKING CHANGE: description
#   Reviewed-by: name
